data.description: This house has a fantastic spacious floor plan, 4 bedrooms, 2baths, Master Suite w/vaulted ceilings, huge 14x12 walk-in closet, private master bath w/jacuzzi & separate shower. The Kitchen checks all the boxes, large with lots of cabinets and countertop space.  The yard is ready to create memories for all your year round needs, tiered deck and plenty of space in the fenced backyard. 2 furnace & AC units. 2 car detached garage with long driveway. Close to North Dunes nature preserve and North-point Marina and Minutes to downtown Zion.
